IPD-IMGT/HLA Release 3.29.0.1

IPD-IMGT/HLA Release 3.29.0.1

IPD-IMGT/HLA Release 3.29.0.1
The following changes have been made to the IPD-IMGT/HLA Database since
the release of 3.29.0. There have been no changes to the CDS sequences,
which would result in allele name changes.

The following sequences: HLA-A*66:28N, HLA-B*59:10N, MICA*015,
MICA*017, MICA*068, MICA*083, MICA*084 have had sequence feature
coordinates corrected in the XML and hla.dat files, these changes do
not impact on the sequence, only the markup used in certain files.

The numbering of the genomic alignments of HLA-DQA1 was incorrect and
has been updated in the text and online alignments.

The following changes have been made to the genomic sequences of a
number of Class II alleles.

Commas in the genomic alignment for HLA-DQA1*05:05:01:03 have been
corrected to full stops.
